quran[16]{c,v,t,f}:
  38,1,"Sọ̄d. (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú háràfí náà.)<sup>1</sup> Allāhu fi al-Ƙur’ān tí ó kún fún ìrántí bura.","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah; 2:1."
  38,2,"Síbẹ̀síbẹ̀ àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ wà nínú ìgbéraga àti ìyapa (òdodo).",""
  38,3,"Mélòó mélòó nínú àwọn ìran tí A ti parẹ́ ṣíwájú wọn. Nígbà náà, wọ́n kígbe (fún ìrànlọ́wọ́) nígbà tí kò sí ibùsásí kan.",""
  38,4,"Wọ́n ṣèèmọ̀ pé olùkìlọ̀ kan nínú wọn wá bá wọn. Àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ sì wí pé: “Èyí ni òpìdán, òpùrọ́.”",""
  38,5,"Ṣé ó máa sọ àwọn òrìṣà di Ọlọ́hun Ọ̀kan ṣoṣo tí a gbọ́dọ̀ jọ́sìn fún ní ọ̀nà òdodo? Dájúdájú èyí mà ni n̄ǹkan ìyanu.",""
  38,6,"Àwọn aṣíwájú nínú wọn sì lọ (káà kiri láti wí fún àwọn ọmọlẹ́yìn wọn) pé: “Ẹ máa bá (ìbọ̀rìṣà) lọ, kí ẹ sì dúró ṣinṣin ti àwọn òrìṣà yín. Dájúdájú èyí (jíjẹ́ ọ̀kan ṣoṣo Allāhu) ni n̄ǹkan tí wọ́n ń gbàlérò (láti fi pa àwọn òrìṣà yín run).",""
  38,7,"Àwa kò gbọ́ èyí nínú ẹ̀sìn ìkẹ́yìn (ìyẹn, ẹ̀sìn nasọ̄rọ̄)<sup>1</sup>. Èyí kò jẹ́ kiní kan bí kò ṣe àdápa irọ́.","[1] Ìyẹn ni pé, ẹ̀sìn nasọ̄rọ̄ tó kẹ́yìn dé gan-an kò pe Ọlọ́hun ní Ọ̀kan ṣoṣo. Mẹ́ta lọ́kan ni ìgbàgbọ́ rẹ̀. Èyí túmọ̀ sí pé, ẹ̀sìn ’Islām nìkan l’ó mọ Ọlọ́hun ní Ọ̀kan ṣoṣo."
  38,8,"Ṣé Wọ́n sọ (tírà) Ìrántí kalẹ̀ fún un láààrin wa ni?” Rárá, wọ́n wà nínú iyèméjì nípa (tírà) Ìrántí Mi (tí Mo sọ̀kalẹ̀ ni). Rárá, wọn kò tí ì tọ́ ìyà Mi wò ni.",""
  38,9,"Tàbí tiwọn ni àwọn ilé ọ̀rọ̀ Olúwa rẹ, Alágbára, Ọlọ́rẹ?",""
  38,10,"Tàbí tiwọn ni ìjọba àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀ àti ohun tí ń bẹ láààrin méjèèjì? Tí ó bá rí bẹ́ẹ̀, kí wọn wá àwọn ọ̀nà láti fi gùnkè wá (bá Wa).",""
  38,11,"A máa ṣẹ́gun ọmọ ogun tó wà níbẹ̀ yẹn nínú ọmọ ogun oníjọ.<sup>1</sup>","[1] Èyí ni àdéhùn ìṣẹ́gun fún Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -àti àwọn mùsùlùmí lórí àwọn ọ̀tá ’Islām. Irú àdéhùn yìí tún wà nínú sūrah al-Ƙọmọr; 54:45."
  38,12,"Àwọn ìjọ Nūh, ìjọ ‘Ād àti Fir‘aon, eléèkàn, wọ́n pe òdodo ní irọ́ ṣíwájú wọn.",""
  38,13,"Ìjọ Thamūd, ìjọ Lūt àti àwọn ará ’Aekah, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn (tún ni) àwọn ìjọ (tó pe òdodo ní irọ́).",""
  38,14,"Kò sí ẹnì kan nínú wọn tí kò pe àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ ní òpùrọ́. Nítorí náà, ìyà Mi sì kò lé wọn lórí.",""
  38,15,"Àwọn wọ̀nyí kò retí kiní kan bí kò ṣe igbe ẹyọ kan, tí kò níí ní ìdádúró.<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ìyẹn ni pé, igbe ẹyọ kan ló máa pa wọ́n run. Kò níí sí igbe mìíràn mọ́ lẹ́yìn rẹ̀ fun ìparun wọn. Ẹ̀ẹ̀ kan gbọ̀n-ọ́n ni ìparun wọn."
  38,16,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Olúwa wa, yára fi ìwé iṣẹ́ wa (àti ìpín ẹ̀san wa) lé wa lọ́wọ́ ṣíwájú Ọjọ́ ìṣírò-iṣẹ́.”",""
